        "en": "1. Introduction to the course<br>2. 7 stages of design innovation thinking<br>3. Ways to find opportunities<br>4. Method of analyzing opportunity points<br>5. User research methodology<br>6. User research data analysis<br>7. Conceptual thinking method<br>8. Concept evaluation method<br>9. Case study of creative thinking process"
